WEBVTT

1
00:40:17.060 --> 00:40:19.050 
他们是善良的
They are gentle,

2
00:40:19.090 --> 00:40:21.060 
友爱的
loving,

3
00:40:21.090 --> 00:40:22.680 
诚信的
faithful,

4
00:40:22.730 --> 00:40:25.290 
不虚伪矫诈
lacking in all guile and trickery.

5
00:40:28.570 --> 00:40:30.930 
不懂任何阴谋诡计
The words denoting lying,

6
00:40:30.970 --> 00:40:32.940 
谎言，贪婪
deceit, greed,

7
00:40:32.970 --> 00:40:35.230 
嫉妒、诽谤、宽恕
envy, slander and forgiveness

8
00:40:35.270 --> 00:40:37.640 
从不曾在他们的词典里出现
have never been heard.

9
00:40:40.140 --> 00:40:42.670 
他们不会羡慕
They have no jealousy,

10
00:40:42.710 --> 00:40:45.110 
没有占有的概念
no sense of possession.

